```plantuml
@startuml YashwantChauhan_SDL

actor User
participant "Web Interface" as WebInterface
participant "Django Server" as DjangoServer
participant "Random Forest Classifier" as Classifier
participant "Database" as DB

User -> WebInterface: Access Web Interface
WebInterface -> DjangoServer: Request Login/Signup
DjangoServer -> DB: Query User Authentication
DB --> DjangoServer: Authentication Result
DjangoServer --> WebInterface: Login/Signup Result

User -> WebInterface: Upload Traffic File
WebInterface -> DjangoServer: Send File for Processing
DjangoServer -> Classifier: Classify Network Traffic
Classifier --> DjangoServer: Classification Result

DjangoServer -> DB: Store Detection History
DjangoServer --> WebInterface: Display Results & Recommendations

User -> WebInterface: View History
WebInterface -> DjangoServer: Request Detection History
DjangoServer -> DB: Query Detection History
DB --> DjangoServer: Detection History Data
DjangoServer --> WebInterface: Show Detection History

@enduml
```